@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About";
}

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h2 class="text-primary">@ViewBag.Title</h2>

    <p class="lead">
        The Disaster Alleviation Foundation is dedicated to offering timely and effective support during times of crisis. Our mission is to mobilize resources swiftly and efficiently to address the needs of those affected by disasters.
    </p>

    <p>
        We operate on the principle of transparency and accountability, ensuring that every donation is utilized to its fullest potential. Our platform allows us to meticulously track donations, whether they be goods such as clothing and non-perishable food items or monetary contributions. This system helps us ensure that resources are allocated where they are most needed, and we can provide detailed reports on the distribution of aid.
    </p>

    <p>
        Our donors are an essential part of our efforts. Individuals, companies, organizations, and even government entities contribute to our cause. We value the privacy of our supporters, and donors have the option to remain anonymous if they prefer.
    </p>

    <p>
        With a commitment to transparency, we strive to maintain open communication with our donors and the public about how their contributions are making a difference. Our goal is to foster trust and confidence in our operations and to demonstrate the positive impact of every contribution.
    </p>

    <p class="font-italic">
        At the Disaster Alleviation Foundation, we believe that every effort counts, and together, we can make a significant difference in the lives of those in need.
    </p>
</div>